            'title'       => __( 'Event Single Page Template', 'cgb' ),
            'description' => _x( 'Default page layout of event.', 'Block pattern description', 'cgb' ),
            'categories'  => array('page-templates'),
            'keywords'    => array('event', 'template'),
            'content'     => "<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://www-new.ixiasoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/IxiatalksEp10-visuheader-scaled.jpg\",\"id\":4732,\"dimRatio\":0,\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.50\",\"y\":\"0.47\"},\"minHeight\":200,\"contentPosition\":\"center center\",\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"background-image:url(http://www-new.ixiasoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/IxiatalksEp10-visuheader-scaled.jpg);min-height:200px;background-position:50% 47%\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"placeholder\":\"Write title…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"backgroundColor\":\"theme-secondary\",\"textColor\":\"theme-white\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-theme-white-color has-theme-secondary-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"#register\">Register Now</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-heading-style-1\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left is-style-heading-style-1\">A LOOK AT THE CCMS MARKETPLACE WITH TONY WHITE</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In this webinar host Sydney Jones will interview Ars Logica Founder Tony White about the state of the CCMS marketplace. The presentation will look at the present and future of the CCMS/DITA landscape, discuss some of the impacts COVID-19 has had on the documentation industry, cover important considerations to take into account when selecting a CCMS, and highlight some of Tony White’s key findings in his 2019 analysis of the CCMS industry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><em>What are the current trends in the DITA marketplace?</em></li><li><em>Which industries are most likely to benefit from adopting a CCMS?</em></li><li><em>How has COVID-19 affected technical documentation across the globe?</em></li><li><em>What makes&nbsp;IXIASOFT CCMS a good fit for certain organizations</em>?</li><li><em>What differentiates IXIASOFT CCMS from other CCMSs on the market?</em></li><li><em>Can you predict any future trends within DITA or the CCMS industry?</em></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-heading-style-1\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left is-style-heading-style-1\">GUEST SPEAKER</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":50296,\"width\":100,\"height\":100} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://www.ixiasoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Tony-White.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-50296\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TONY WHITE<br><em><span class=\"has-inline-color has-theme-secondary-color\">Founder, Ars Logica</span></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-heading-style-1\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left is-style-heading-style-1\" id=\"register\">REGISTER FOR THE RECORDING</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe class=\"pardotform\" src=\"https://go.ixiasoft.com/l/521231/2020-10-06/3lz27s\" type=\"text/html\" allowtransparency=\"true\" style=\"border: 0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->",
        )
    );

